        chaptermarkers
        ==================
        
        
        .. image:: https://img.shields.io/pypi/v/python_boilerplate.svg
                :target: https://pypi.python.org/pypi/python_boilerplate
        
        .. image:: https://img.shields.io/travis/fgriberi/python_boilerplate.svg
